main event: A civilian reported observing a satellite (Echo I) in the Wyomissing, Pennsylvania area on July 3, 1967.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 5 minutes and 52 seconds,The course of the observed object was N-NE,There was no physical evidence or photographs of the event,The observation was classified as a satellite sighting (Echo I) by the authorities,The report form did not reveal any other witnesses despite stating that several people might have seen the same UFO.
witness description: civilian who filled out the observation form
